name: Stargrail's Chosen
desc:
An honest youth who has equipped himself with the remains of Mekstrosities.
Having long since admired the "Star Hero" told in stories around the Celestial Forest since ancient times, he accepted Fairy Ries's request, and set out on a journey to to release the Seven Starrelics with his comrades who have also been gifted by the light.
"Starlight Hero
Raise Your Sword and Gather the Light
You Must Vanquish the Great Darkness"
